 century. It is most famous as the name of Dante's beloved, and is borne by the elder (  b. 1988 ) of the Duke of York's daughters."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Beatrice Theydon was born about 1191 as the daughter of Henry de Theydon. She married William de Gernon before 1208, in Europe. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 1 daughter. She died in 1269, in Essex, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 79."},"et":{"Abt 1191–1269":"umbes 1191–1269","1191–1269":"1191–1269","1190–1258":"1190–1258","1208–1266":"1208–1266","1220–1274":"1220–1274","1231–Male":"1231–Surnud","1168–1217":"1168–1217","1190":"1190","1220":"1220","1231":"1231","1274":"1274","before 1208":"enne 1208","abt 1231":"umbes 1231","1191":"1191","1217":"1217","about 1208":"umbes 1208","1269":"1269","1258":"1258","4 December 1258":"4. detsember 1258","1168":"1168","1266":"1266","Abt 1191":"umbes 1191","1208":"1208","Ongar, Essex, England":"Ongar, Essex, England","Theydon, Essex, England":"Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Bakewell, Derbyshire, England":"Bakewell, Derbyshire, England","East Thorpe, Essex, England":"Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Tidewell, Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Europe":"Europe","Bakewell Circuit, Derbyshire, England":"Bakewell Circuit, Derbyshire, England"},"fi":{"Abt 1191–1269":"noin 1191–1269","1191–1269":"1191–1269","1190–1258":"1190–1258","1208–1266":"1208–1266","1220–1274":"1220–1274","1231–Male":"1231–Kuollut","1168–1217":"1168–1217","1190":"1190","1220":"1220","1231":"1231","1274":"1274","before 1208":"ennen vuotta 1208","abt 1231":"noin 1231","1191":"1191","1217":"1217","about 1208":"noin 1208","1269":"1269","1258":"1258","4 December 1258":"4. joulukuuta 1258","1168":"1168","1266":"1266","Abt 1191":"noin 1191","1208":"1208","Ongar, Essex, England":"Ongar, Essex, England","Theydon, Essex, England":"Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Bakewell, Derbyshire, England":"Bakewell, Derbyshire, England","East Thorpe, Essex, England":"Essex, Englan